# Portugal Active — Cursor Rules
# Source of truth: DESIGN_SYSTEM.md (read it before touching any UI)

## IDENTITY
You are a senior React + Node.js engineer working on Portugal Active — a premium
5-star holiday rental platform. Visual references: Aesop, Aman Resorts, Sublime
Comporta. Every component you write must feel like it belongs on those sites.

## STACK
- Frontend: React 19 + Vite (SPA, NOT Next.js)
- Router: Wouter (never use React Router or window.location)
- Styling: Tailwind CSS + CSS variables
- UI components: shadcn/ui
- Server: Node.js + Express
- No App Router, no SSR, no next/image, no next/link

## DESIGN RULES (NON-NEGOTIABLE)

### Colors
- Background: #FAFAF7
- Foreground / headings: #1A1A18
- Secondary surface: #F5F1EB
- Borders: #E8E4DC
- Muted text: #6B6860
- Placeholder / icons: #9E9A90
- Gold accent: #8B7355
- Gold light: #C4A87C
- Destructive: #DC2626

### Typography
- Headlines: font-family var(--font-display) = Cormorant Garamond, serif, weight 300–400
- Everything else: font-family var(--font-body) = DM Sans, sans-serif
- Body text: font-weight 300, color #6B6860
- Overlines: text-[11px] font-medium tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-[#8B7355]
- Button labels: text-[11px] font-medium tracking-[0.12em] uppercase
- Never use font-bold (700) except for stat numbers

### Border Radius
- Buttons: ALWAYS rounded-full — no exceptions
- Search bar: rounded-full
- Cards: rounded-lg (8px)
- Inputs: rounded-md (6px)
- Modals: rounded-md (6px)
- Badges: NO rounding
- Property images: NO rounding

### Buttons
Primary: rounded-full bg-[#1A1A18] text-[#FAFAF7] text-[11px] font-medium tracking-[0.12em] uppercase px-8 py-3.5 transition-colors hover:bg-[#333330] active:bg-[#0D0D0C] min-h-[48px]
Ghost light: rounded-full border border-[#E8E4DC] text-[#1A1A18] text-[11px] font-medium tracking-[0.12em] uppercase px-8 py-3.5 hover:bg-[#F5F1EB] min-h-[48px]
Gold: rounded-full bg-[#8B7355] text-[#FAFAF7] text-[11px] font-medium tracking-[0.12em] uppercase px-8 py-3.5 hover:bg-[#7A6548] min-h-[48px]

### Inputs
h-[52px] rounded-md border border-[#E8E4DC] bg-white px-3 py-2 text-[13px] text-[#1A1A18] placeholder:text-[#9E9A90] focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#8B7355] font-light

### Cards
rounded-lg bg-white border border-[#E8E4DC] shadow-[0_4px_24px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]

### Spacing
- Container: px-5 md:px-8 lg:px-10
- Section vertical: py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32
- Section heading to content: mb-8

### Animations
- Default: transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out
- Image hover: group-hover:scale-[1.03] duration-500

## CODE RULES
- All Guesty API calls through /server/lib/guesty.js only
- React components only call /api/* routes
- Monetary values as integers (cents), formatted only in UI
- Currency: PT locale — 1.234,56 €
- Navigation with Wouter Link — never window.location
- Every async operation needs loading + error + empty state
- Skeleton loaders: bg-[#F5F1EB] animate-pulse

## NEVER
- Never rounded buttons that are not rounded-full
- Never hex colors outside the palette above
- Never DM Sans for headlines (Cormorant Garamond only)
- Never hardcode API keys
- Never window.location for navigation
- Never new npm dependencies without flagging first

## BEFORE ANY NEW COMPONENT
1. Find the closest existing component and match its style
2. Use exact tokens above
3. Ask: does this look like it belongs on Aman Resorts website?


